tool_description: An API that provides easy and efficient access to both OpenSea's GraphQL API and OpenSea's Testnet GraphQL API.
name: OpenSea GraphQL with Testnets
title: OpenSea GraphQL with Testnets

api_list.name: Opensea GraphQL
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://opensea-graphql-with-testnets1.p.rapidapi.com/__api/graphQL"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "opensea-graphql-with-testnets1.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
